  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这套系统画一个架构图，核心是用户从入口开始，能完成注册和登录两大流程。我先把顶层结构理一下：入口层叫Inicio del App，里面要放Etcd集群作为配置中心，然后分两条主线——注册走Redis缓存，登录走Ingress控制器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inicio_del_App",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Registrarse",
        "Iniciar"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以顶层是一个子图，里面A节点是Etcd集群，然后A到B是注册流程，A到C是登录流程。B和C分别对应Redis和Ingress控制器，对吧？这两个动作标签我记为Registrarse和Iniciar Sesión？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "Registrarse",
        "Iniciar Sesión"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，标签用西班牙语，Registrarse是注册，Iniciar Sesión是登录。接下来注册流程要展开一个子图，里面包含用户填写的所有字段：Nome Completo、Nome de Usuário、Data de Nascimento、Género、Email、Número de Telefone和Senha。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registro",
        "Nome_Completo",
        "Nome_de_Usuario",
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Género",
        "Email",
        "Número_de_Telefone",
        "Senha"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这些字段都是B节点Redis缓存的下级节点吗？还有，我注意到Nome Completo、Nome de Usuário、Data de Nascimento和Número de Telefone后面好像带了基础设施标注，比如Infra_WorkerNode、Infra_LoadBalancer这些？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "Nome_Completo",
        "Nome_de_Usuario",
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Número_de_Telefone",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，那几个字段需要关联后端基础设施。Nome Completo落在Worker节点上，Nome de Usuário和Data de Nascimento走负载均衡，但Data de Nascimento其实也要回写Redis，Número de Telefone要同步到Etcd集群做唯一性校验。Género、Email和Senha是纯业务字段，不用挂基础设施。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Nome_Completo",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Nome_de_Usuario",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Número_de_Telefone",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Género",
        "Email",
        "Senha"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，注册子图已经画好了。现在处理登录流程，也是一个子图对吧？从C节点Ingress控制器下来，应该只有两个字段：Usuario Email和Senha？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Login",
        "C",
        "Usuario_Email",
        "Senha"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，登录要简单很多。Usuario Email需要经过负载均衡去查询用户服务，Senha是本地校验。所以Usuario Email要标注Infra_LoadBalancer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Usuario_Email",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Senha"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。我整体检查一遍：顶层Inicio del App包含Etcd、Redis、Ingress三个核心组件；注册子图七个字段，其中四个挂了基础设施；登录子图两个字段，Usuario Email挂了负载均衡。结构对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inicio_del_App",
        "Registro",
        "Login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Data de Nascimento的基础设施标错了。我刚才说错了——它不应该再挂Redis，因为父节点B已经是Redis了，重复了。让我重新理：Nome Completo→WorkerNode，Nome de Usuário→LoadBalancer，Data de Nascimento→LoadBalancer，Número de Telefone→EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，已修正Data de Nascimento的标注为Infra_LoadBalancer，去掉了Redis的重复标记。现在注册子图的四个基础设施关联都准确了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data_de_Nascimento",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再确认一下登录流程的命名——我用的Usuario Email，中间有空格吗？还是下划线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Usuario_Email"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "目前是Usuario_Email，下划线连接。需要改成空格吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Usuario_Email"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "保持下划线吧，和注册字段的命名风格统一。另外我补充一个细节：登录的Senha和注册的Senha虽然同名，但是不同子图里的独立节点，这个没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Senha",
        "Registro",
        "Login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，Mermaid里不同子图的节点ID是独立的，即使显示名称相同也不会冲突。注册Senha在Registro子图，登录Senha在Login子图。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Senha",
        "Registro",
        "Login"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后确认顶层交互：A到B的边标签是Registrarse，A到C是Iniciar Sesión，注意Iniciar和Sesión之间要有空格。这是西班牙语的习惯写法。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "Registrarse",
        "Iniciar Sesión"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部完成。最终结构：顶层Inicio del App子图包含Etcd集群，分出注册和登录两条线；注册子图七个字段带四个基础设施标注；登录子图两个字段，Usuario Email走负载均衡。所有边标签和节点命名已按西班牙语规范设置。",
